the overall GPU hours for training the SuperTrans-
former and the searched SubTransformer. We also 
calculate the cloud computing costs with differ-
ent modes: "preemptable" is cheaper ($0.74/h)

Table 2: Comparisons of latency, model size, FLOPs, BLEU and training cost in terms of CO 2 emissions (lbs) and 
cloud computing cost (USD) for Transformer, the Evolved Transformer and HAT. The training cost estimation is 
adapted from Strubell et al. (2019). The training time is for one Nvidia V100 GPU, and the latency is measured on 
the Raspberry Pi ARM CPU. The cloud computing cost is based on AWS.
